text: <@U02F90CRQ>:  henry barking a lot - anything that helps him? i petted for a long time but he would still bark. :simple_smile:
Shit.  I shouldn't have left like that.  His routine is all out of whack so I shouldn't be surprised he didn't stay calm while I was gone.  Thanks for looking after him.
<@U02F90CRQ>: did you grab him? Folks are heading out.
I did. We split at about 6. Sorry for the ruckus. I won't try to sneak out for a ride on a day when I have Henry. He didn't know WTF was going on.
Was one of the last ones out - wanted to make sure you're good.
Thanks for looking out. I am indeed good. See you guys in the AM.
